    <h1 class="m-4 color-theme">About us</h1>

    <div class="bg-white m-4 p-4 shadow">
        <ul class="fs-5">
            <li>Welcome to Zero Hunger, a dedicated food donation management system committed to reducing food waste and alleviating hunger in our communities. Our platform connects donors with surplus food to local food banks, shelters, and charities that serve those in need.</li>
            <li>We, at Zero Hunger, provide food to poor people across the country.</li>
            <li>Our main aim is to eliminate hunger and satisfy the food needs of needy people by providing them food from our donors.</li>
            <!-- <li>We envision a world where food waste is minimized, and all individuals have access to nutritious meals. Through innovation, collaboration, and community engagement, we strive to build a hunger-free future.</li> -->
			<li>Our dedicated team works tirelessly to identify areas with the greatest need and to establish strong relationships with local organizations. This collaborative effort allows us to maximize the impact of our food distribution programs.</li>
            <li>In addition to food distribution, Zero Hunger also focuses on raising awareness about food insecurity and advocating for policy changes to address the root causes of hunger. We believe that by educating the public and influencing legislation, we can create a more just and equitable food system.</li>
            <!-- <li>Through our educational initiatives, we aim to empower individuals and communities to take action against food waste and hunger. From workshops and seminars to community events, we provide valuable resources and support to those who want to make a difference.</li> -->
